@startuml
autonumber
actor User
participant "Gesture Recognition Module" as GestureRecognitionModule
participant "Face Recognition Module" as FaceRecognitionModule
participant "Hand Tracking Module" as HandTrackingModule
participant "Single-Hand Interaction Module" as SingleHandInteractionModule
participant "Customization Module" as CustomizationModule
participant "Real-Time Collaboration Module" as RealTimeCollaborationModule
participant "Image Processing Module" as ImageProcessingModule
participant "Background Subtraction Module" as BackgroundSubtractionModule
participant "Threading Module" as ThreadingModule
participant "Multiprocessing Module" as MultiprocessingModule
participant "Latency Optimization Module" as LatencyOptimizationModule
participant "Environmental Adaptation Module" as EnvironmentalAdaptationModule
GestureRecognitionModule ->> HandTrackingModule : Trigger hand tracking
HandTrackingModule -> SingleHandInteractionModule : Enable single-hand interaction
FaceRecognitionModule ->> HandTrackingModule : Trigger hand tracking
HandTrackingModule ->> ImageProcessingModule : Process hand movement
ImageProcessingModule ->> BackgroundSubtractionModule : Separate moving parts from background
BackgroundSubtractionModule -> GestureRecognitionModule : Update gesture recognition
CustomizationModule -> GestureRecognitionModule : Update gesture recognition
HandTrackingModule ->> ImageProcessingModule : Process hand movement
ImageProcessingModule ->> RealTimeCollaborationModule : Enable real-time collaboration
BackgroundSubtractionModule -> GestureRecognitionModule : Update gesture recognition
ThreadingModule ->> MultiprocessingModule : Enable parallel execution
MultiprocessingModule ->> LatencyOptimizationModule : Optimize latency
LatencyOptimizationModule ->> RealTimeCollaborationModule : Enable real-time collaboration
EnvironmentalAdaptationModule ->> RealTimeCollaborationModule : Adapt to environment
@enduml